  "texts": [
    "Synergy between Big Data and AI for Improved AnalyticsThe interaction between Big Data and AI has shown remarkable improvements in predictive analytics.Research indicates that training AI systems on large datasets enhances accuracy in forecasting and decision support by 40% [3].",
    "This synergy facilitates reliable predictive analytics and optimized data profiling.",
    "AI's capabilities in anomaly detection and data classification further enhance data quality, enabling faster workflow execution.",
    "Future research could expand on decision optimization using Generative AI in workflows, investigating its scalability and effectiveness across diverse enterprise scenarios [3].",
    "Generative AI in Financial Market PredictionGenerative AI's application in financial market prediction has demonstrated significant advancements.Leveraging Big Data, these systems have improved market forecasting accuracy by over 25% [4]."
